have shown up near my village..."

situation, but it seems to be happening all over this
region, so it looks like I'll have to wait."
Receptionist: "Welcome, how may I assist you today?"

Tina: "I've come to report the completion of a task Selphie
had requested of me."

Receptionist: "You must be Tina-sama, correct? Please,
Selphie-sama is waiting for you in the reception room on the
second floor."
